en_70571_0	The met department states that an atmospheric disturbance will affect the weather over the country causing more showers.
en_70571_1	Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in the Northern, North central, Eastern and Uva provinces and in the Hambantota district.
en_70571_2	Showers or thundershowers will be fairly widespread during the afternoon and night.
en_70571_3	Fairly heavy falls about 100 mili meters are also likely at some places.
